    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for the road? I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s been kept in really solid shape over the years. It runs beautifully, the interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more miles with a new owner. Come see it for yourself\u2014I think you\u2019ll really like how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
