    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to address factory floor pan fatigue, and the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings for precise lateral stability. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car that maintains excellent throttle response and structural rigidity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well.",
