    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable car that balances performance with everyday utility. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and it has a documented history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though close inspection reveals minor road rash on the front bumper and a few small surface scratches typical of a carefully driven car. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The upholstery is free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all gauges and electronics\u2014including the cold A/C and premium audio system\u2014functioning perfectly. The tires are recent and provide excellent grip, ensuring this car is ready for the road immediately. This is a solid, honest vehicle that delivers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
