      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure consistent performance and long-term reliability. With a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to inspect the superior handling and robust engineering that define this exceptional model. Secure this high-value acquisition today.",
