      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. Perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town! It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014definitely ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
