      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis is supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing excellent lateral grip and composure. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system remain within tight tolerances. The subframe and bushings are in solid condition, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
